title: Cannot Transfer Account to Oceania
body:
I created this account long before the Oceania servers were a thing, stopped playing around the time that they came up and the free transfers were given. I created a smurf to play on and off as I didn't really feel like playing particularly seriously again, but over the last few days I've been wanting to play more and  with the champion/skin pool that I've already accumulated (which are pretty numerous) but it seems like I can't get a transfer. It's simply not in the store.

 What do?

replies.body:
Hi

What region are you trying to transfer from? I checked the NA store (per the account you have posted under) and it looks like it is enabled there.

Let me know and I'll see what I can do to help! :)

Cheers
Mindstar
